Joey And The Taste Test

LUCY LIU ("CHARLIE'S ANGELS") GUESTSTARS AS JOEY'S PRODUCER LAUREN-- While shooting his new show "Deep Powder," Joey starts to fall for his co-star daughter Katie. (Danneel Harris) Lauren (gueat star Lucy Liu) tries to persuade Joey that relationships at work are not a good idea, while coming on to him herself. Meanwhile, Gina agrees to teach Alex how to make her famous lasagna after raving about how wonderful it tastes. Joey and Michael (Paulo Costanzo) are then forced to be judges for a lasagna-making contest between Gina and Alex. TV-14
